data.description: Gorgeous 3 Bedroom home in Sienna Village! Downstairs features a formal dining room, amazing kitchen with beautiful countertops, tons of cabinetry and breakfast area. Upstairs has a spacious game room and two huge secondary bedrooms with an additional bathroom. The backyard is huge, big enough to put in a pool to enjoy your family parties. This home is truly a gem!! Please come set up your appointment today you won't be disappointed. “This home is eligible for a grant of up to $5000 towards your purchase if you are a qualified buyer.”
